@* The other half of the MUTUAL cycle (CycleMutual.razor). Its own guard is false for the Label
   Alpha passes it, so the Blazor render stops here; the INLINER does not, because it never asks
   what Label is. *@
<em class="beta">@Label@if (Label == "deeper") { <CycleAlpha Label="a" /> }</em>

@code {
    [Parameter] public string Label { get; set; } = "";
}
